name: Elysia
description: Tales of angels and demons have been told for centuries. Until now, the astral plane in which these sols inhabit has been inaccessible to mortal beings. Heaven’s gate has opened, we’ve found a way to travel to the evangelic realm to uncover the secrets that lay within. At the heart of this mysterious world lies the city of Elysia, once called paradise, ravaged through war and famine. With lost sols wandering about, the first to unlock the gate will decide the fate of Elysia.
